'''巴伊·比比亞奧恩·利格卡亞恩·比格卡伊'''（Bai Bibyaon Ligkayan Bigkay；{{bd|約1940年|}}<ref name=Davao>{{Cite web|last=Cortez|first=Kath M.|date=2019-08-14|title=Lumad women, their inter-generational struggle for self-determination|url=http://davaotoday.com/main/culture-2/lumad-women-their-inter-generational-struggle-for-self-determination/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108020248/http://davaotoday.com/main/culture-2/lumad-women-their-inter-generational-struggle-for-self-determination/|archive-date=2020-11-08|access-date=2020-06-05|website=Davao Today|dead-url=no}}</ref> ）是[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]部落首領與環保主義者，為[[民答那峨島|民答那峨島]]{{tsl|en|Lumad|鲁玛德|馬諾博}}部落的第一位、也是迄今唯一一位女性首領<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=February 22, 2017|title=Lumad Leader Bai Bibyaon Ligkayan Bigkay is 2017 UP Gawad Tandang Sora awardee|url=https://www.up.edu.ph/lumad-leader-bai-bibyaon-ligkayan-bigkay-is-2017-up-gawad-tandang-sora-awardee/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605091740/https://www.up.edu.ph/lumad-leader-bai-bibyaon-ligkayan-bigkay-is-2017-up-gawad-tandang-sora-awardee/|archive-date=2020-06-05|access-date=2020-06-05|website=University of the Philippines|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其名中的「巴伊」為民答那峨女性的榮譽頭銜，「比比亞奧恩」則是部落首領的頭銜<ref>{{cite news |title=Bai Bigkay is Gawad Tandang Sora awardee |accessdate=June 6, 2020 |url=https://upd.edu.ph/bai-bigkay-is-gawad-tandang-sora-awardee/ |publisher=University of the Philippines |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116123602/https://upd.edu.ph/bai-bigkay-is-gawad-tandang-sora-awardee/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自1994年起比格卡伊便是一名活躍的原住民權益倡議者，捍衛馬諾博人的傳統領域{{le|潘托浪山脉|Pantaron Mountain Range}}，對抗伐木對此區域環境的破壞與族人面臨的[[種族滅絕|種族滅絕]]威脅<ref name=":0" /><ref name=Sora>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2017-02-24|title=UP CSWCD names Bai Bibyaon Ligkayan Bigkay 2017 Gawad Tandang Sora honoree|url=https://kodao.org/up-cswcd-names-bai-bibyaon-ligkayan-bigkay-2017-gawad-tandang-sora-honoree/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202124145/https://kodao.org/up-cswcd-names-bai-bibyaon-ligkayan-bigkay-2017-gawad-tandang-sora-honoree/|archive-date=2020-12-02|access-date=2020-06-05|website=Kodao Productions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年族人受地方武裝勢力攻擊時，她率族人遷至城市中<ref name=Davao/>。

2017年，[[菲律賓大學|菲律賓大學]]頒發坦當梭拉獎（Gawad Tandang Sora）給比格卡伊以表揚她為領導少數民族爭取權益與尊嚴的努力，將她譽為「鄉間的{{le|梅秋拉·阿基諾|Melchora Aquino}}」<ref name=Sora/>。2018年，她獲頒第五屆環境英雄獎（Gawad Bayani ng Kalikasan）<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Salamat|first=Marya|date=2018-03-17|title=‘We’re all challenged to defend the environment’ - Bibiaon Bigkay|url=https://www.bulatlat.com/2018/03/17/challenged-defend-environment-bibiaon-bigkay-bayani-ng-kalikasan-distinguished-awardee/|access-date=2020-06-26|website=Bulatlat|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117122352/https://www.bulatlat.com/2018/03/17/challenged-defend-environment-bibiaon-bigkay-bayani-ng-kalikasan-distinguished-awardee/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

